casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Daraian Lee WINFIELD, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 157063
COA: 334396 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 1, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the November 28, 2017 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the question presented should be reviewed by this Court.
